Overview:
A full‑stack ecommerce web application built with Django and Bootstrap, replicating the look and feel of Flipkart/Amazon. Features include product listings, hero banners, category strips, horizontal scroll sections, and OTP‑based login for secure authentication.

Features:
Full‑width hero banners and modular product sections.

Category strips with horizontal scrolling.

OTP‑based login and authentication flow.

Responsive design with Bootstrap for mobile, tablet, and desktop.

Scalable backend with Django querysets and views.

Deployment ready with Procfile, requirements.txt, and runtime.txt.

Tech Stack:
Backend: Django, Python.

Frontend: HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, JavaScript.

Database: PostgreSQL / MySQL.

Deployment: Render / Railway (Gunicorn + Whitenoise).

Version Control: GitHub.

Project Structure:
ecommerce/
│── manage.py
│── Procfile
│── runtime.txt
│── requirements.txt
│── ecommerce/        # Project settings, wsgi.py
│── store/            # App with models, views, templates
│── static/           # CSS, JS, images
│── templates/        # HTML templates

